  "page": "Gundor Goodbrother",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> Gundor Goodbrother's canon status is unclear: the character is cited only in an earlier version of the Iron Islands section from <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Gundor_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Gundor-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Gundor Goodbrother</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (draft)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gundor Goodbrother</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a> who founded <a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gundor_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, Gundor founded <a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a> on the coast of the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/House_Casterly\" title=\"House Casterly\">House Casterly</a> still held <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Gundor_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Gundor-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gundor_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Gundor-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Gundor_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Gundor_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/&amp;do=findComment&amp;comment=8946110\">The ASOIAF wiki thread &#8211; Comment by Ran (June 2, 2023)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215601\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.261 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 385/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2334/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5459/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 602/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 702/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.3 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  251.229      1 -total\n 98.08%  246.411      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.99%  243.675      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.69%   29.377     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.21%    8.060      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.09%    2.739      1 Template:Notice\n  0.86%    2.158      1 Template:Mbox\n  0.60%    1.504      1 Template:References\n  0.43%    1.078      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved 